# Email Server Settings (SMTP) for sending OTPs
# How to get your Google App Password:
# 1. Open your Google Account settings (https://myaccount.google.com).
# 2. Go to "Security" -> Turn on "2-Step Verification".
# 3. Search for "App passwords" in the search bar.
# 4. Generate a new password (select App: "Other (custom name)", e.g. "Data Quality Platform").
# 5. Copy the 16-character code and paste it below inside SMTP_PASSWORD.
# 6. Change SMTP_USER to your Gmail address.
